{"tid":568279,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冷鋒明殺到！料日半急跌7度","createTime":"2018-02-21T15:38:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T15:44:57.000Z","uid":1121,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"42e0e76e4884b20a0d4bd9021dd4ee3b4d89e3cf","tid":568279,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:38:06.000Z","msg":"本港經歷相當溫暖的農曆新年假期後，明日和後日將再度轉涼。天文台預計，一道冷鋒周四（22日）會抵達華南沿岸，隨後的東北季候風將帶來相當清涼的天氣；本港市區會由今日下午最高的21&deg;C，跌至明日深夜和後日早上最低的14&deg;C，降至相當清涼的水平，即一日半顯著下跌7度。<br />\n<br />\n天色方面，本港今日將大致多雲，有一兩陣微雨。早上部分地區能見度頗低；明日則多雲，有幾陣雨，冷鋒過後將由東風轉吹北風，風勢由和緩加強至清勁程度。天文台預料，該季候風在周末期間會逐漸緩和，屆時天色會較為明朗。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180220/large/1519119961_b248.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180220%2Flarge%2F1519119961_b248.png&h=cb06bfd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b65b65ae23d2edff309b95cc13a080aa4b49611a","tid":568279,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:38:19.000Z","msg":"<del><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </del>"},{"pid":"82b52eae252dd7dba911fdfc78b605028c650d6e","tid":568279,"uid":1121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:43:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c25703db61293ddfb264abe17abc1bb03030fe4","tid":568279,"uid":53105,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:44:54.000Z","msg":"14度都冷鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 以為降到7度"},{"pid":"85741803b6a45d4a3aa8d6b093103180eb44a20f","tid":568279,"uid":55192,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T15:44:57.000Z","msg":"下一步：起女女底"}]}